r/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1651385949", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 48582, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1651385949", "stars": 7801, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 156814, "username": "Hanggi", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Hanggi", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/85f6/cdb0/156814_mini.png?m=1499746915", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/85f6/cdb0/156814_normal.png?m=1499746915", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/85f6/cdb0/156814_large.png?m=1499746915", "created": 1453691391, "last_modified": 1499746915}, "last_reply_by": "takashiki", "last_touched": 1651658646, "title": "Mac Windows 一套键鼠控制多台设备解决方案", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/850750", "created": 1651635526, "deleted": 0, "content": "目前一台 Windows 台式机加双显示器，旁边放了一台 mbp ，每次切换键盘太麻烦，准备入一台 Mac mini ，用一套键鼠。\r\n\r\n有没有比较成熟的键鼠显示器切换设备的解决方案，最好不要太多接线。\r\n\r\n目前没找到太好的方案，不行打算用远程桌面访问 mac 。有没有遇到类似问题的，求分享解决方案。", "content_rendered": "<p>目前一台 Windows 台式机加双显示器，旁边放了一台 mbp ，每次切换键盘太麻烦，准备入一台 Mac mini ，用一套键鼠。</p>\n<p>有没有比较成熟的键鼠显示器切换设备的解决方案，最好不要太多接线。</p>\n<p>目前没找到太好的方案，不行打算用远程桌面访问 mac 。有没有遇到类似问题的，求分享解决方案。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1651635576, "replies": 28, "id": 850750}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1651385965", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 9413, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965", "stars": 5059, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 39, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 21672, "username": "fyooo", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/fyooo", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/daa1/7202/21672_mini.png?m=1645146994", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/daa1/7202/21672_normal.png?m=1645146994", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/daa1/7202/21672_large.png?m=1645146994", "created": 1338382558, "last_modified": 1645146994}, "last_reply_by": "clf", "last_touched": 1651659665, "title": "MIUI 可以关闭「新热」和清理内存的消息通知吗?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/850738", "created": 1651631741, "deleted": 0, "content": "原来用的是华为手机，最近换成红米 K50 ，遇到 2 个困惑。\r\n\r\n第一个是一般手机桌面上推是多任务，但是 MIUI 经常出现「新热」，如图：\r\n![p1]( https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24egy1h1w62l5v0fj20ns1egaj6.jpg)\r\n\r\n第二个是清理内存的等手机管家的消息提醒居然不能关闭？！！！\r\n\r\n![p2]( https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24egy1h1w6408792j20ni0gmgls.jpg)\r\n\r\n我知道 iPhone 最好，但是迫于生活压力，不能换手机了，不知道 MIUI 还有没有救?", "content_rendered": "<p>原来用的是华为手机，最近换成红米 K50 ，遇到 2 个困惑。</p>\n<p>第一个是一般手机桌面上推是多任务，但是 MIUI 经常出现「新热」，如图：\n<img alt=\"p1\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24egy1h1w62l5v0fj20ns1egaj6.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>第二个是清理内存的等手机管家的消息提醒居然不能关闭？！！！</p>\n<p><img alt=\"p2\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/e6c9d24egy1h1w6408792j20ni0gmgls.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>我知道 iPhone 最好，但是迫于生活压力，不能换手机了，不知道 MIUI 还有没有救?</p>\n", "last_modified": 1651631741, "replies": 27, "id": 850738}]